==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Immethodical
<hw>Im`me*thod"ic*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not
methodical; without method or systematic arrangement; without order or
regularity; confused.</def> <rj><au>Addison.</au></rj></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Irregular; confused; disoderly; unsystematic;
desultory.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Immethodically</ent>⟦br⟧
